<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id779570ab-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s430h–9"><num value="430h–9">§ 430h–9.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the purposes of sections 430h–6 to 430h–9 of this title.</p>
